{"tid":1684263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"依兩隻畜生喺度搞緊乜？","createTime":"2019-10-31T04:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T04:35:06.000Z","uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0457636e00f746815ef7e3a007b79a30904d874","tid":1684263,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"事實證明十人以下嘅落單狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包圍到佢地有冇後路走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(留意下對方用嘅陣式 永遠有一條路可以後撒 另外衝豬馬路突擊只會車頭車尾範圍跑動追人 只要你沿着馬路跑一定輸 但係你出其不意跑過對面馬路 要誇欄等等 班狗多數唔會追)<br />\n各路手足心態上夠勇武 打狗你知道打邊度最傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋遠攻又係爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n和理非唔夠膽就幫手播鏡頭遮鏡頭 事後死無對證<br />\n你睇返條片有好多呀伯呀叔助攻 <br />\n帶帽同口罩都仲可以認到部份嘅樣 <br />\n呢類和理非幫手檔鏡頭已經好足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打到班狗驚 班狗得<span style=\"color: red;\">2個選擇</span><br />\n近距離用手擲式催淚彈 試圖拉遠距離<br />\n近距離開槍 射橡膠子彈 布袋彈(暫時未見到 唔排除有呢個可能性or開真槍解圍)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cj8x0VE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcj8x0VE.jpg&h=cfac2753&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98585cb682c4ab1639dd3315980903271f9c34c8","tid":1684263,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"佢條女？"},{"pid":"1fccfb7aebd64b641ae97567c9cad8008bd4ac64","tid":1684263,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"同埋每隊嘅一個CID渣機拍片 佢哋多數都便衣着背心 冇防暴裝備 靠班狗保護佢 呢類好仲好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1254d129e13147f7055186abeb7354770bb32ab","tid":1684263,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim